#: ../../source/faq.rst:257
msgid "The holds queue report is divided by libraries and will list the hold only for one library where it is available. For libraries with lots of holds and multiple branches this will prevent multiple libraries pulling the item off the shelf at the same time."
msgstr "預約佇列報表依圖書館排序，列出該圖書可被預約的資料。多筆預約與分館的圖書館，將不會同時拉出該等館藏。"

