msgstr ":ref:`圖書館轉移限制 <library-transfer-limits-label>`"

#: ../../source/faq.rst:268
msgid ":ref:`Transport cost matrix <transport-cost-matrix-label>`"
msgstr ":ref:`轉移成本矩陣 <transport-cost-matrix-label>`"

